name: DiscordianToday

skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Get the current Discordian (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Discordian_calendar) date from Alexa as part of your flash briefing. Updates at midnight central US time.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
